This exception happened when called the app with this .bat:
  chcp 65001
  start "" "c:\Norbi\Programs\Exin\Exin.exe" %*

(When started with "c:\Norbi\Programs\Exin\Exin.exe", it worked)

It's visible from the logs that the "." in the path is really not reliable; this
  .\Config\MainSettings.xml
got translated into 
  C:\Users\Norbert\Config\MainSettings.xml
instead of
c:\Norbi\Programs\Exin\Config\MainSettings.xml







